    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Montreal</placeName>
                <date>21 Apl 65</date>.</p>
            <p>The <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir—</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I don't know whether<lb/> you understood that I expected<lb/> the
                pamphlets (in paper wrappers)<lb/> without the Err<add>?</add>. In any<lb/> case
                please send them on by<lb/> express. <persName>Mrs J H Joseph</persName> is<lb/> now
                on a visit to your city<lb/> but the parcel would be too<lb/> large for her I fear
                as she<lb/> takes but one small trunk,</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>Please send on a detailed<lb/> account of what I owe you,<lb/> making the Sermon
                &amp; Biography<lb/>
                <sic>seperate</sic> items.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I <sic>sympathise</sic> with you<lb/> on the death of the
                    <persName>Reverend<lb/> Lyons</persName> made an <add>השכבה</add> for<lb/> him,
                Did you?</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Remain yours truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">Abraham de Sola</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
